<hl>
<seg id=1> China will use the World Bank's loan to build a communication network for railways </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News agency, Beijing, April 17th, by Tong Qian- Ministry of Railways PRC. Will use the World Bank's loan to build a specific communication network that connect the national railway. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Zhongyi International Tender Offering Company won this auction through an intensive competitive-bidding process, and will provide the Ministry of Railways of PRC with equipment, together with the Auto & Electronic Import & Export Corporation, for 220,000 stored program controlled electronic telephone switching systems. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> An official for the PRC Ministry of Railways presented that, this network establishment is a portion of the national railway communication pivotal engineering project. </seg>
<seg id=5> After this network is established and under operation, it will be a benefit for all railway customers, including those from Hong Kong and Macao, who will be able to use this network to check railway situations, book tickets or spaces for goods in advance, and track down the departure and arrival place of their goods. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> In recent years, China has started to utilize loans from international financial organizations for international competitive bidding and purchasing in the area of capital constructions. </seg>
<seg id=7> This purchase was made according to the international regulations. It was won by the stored program controlled electronic telephone switching system, made by Shanghai Baoer Company and marketing by the Auto & Electronic Import & Export Corporation of the PRC. </seg>
<seg id=8> This is also one of the important orders for the domestic production of the stored program controlled electronic telephone switching system. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> It is said that, the contractors from both sides held a signing ceremony in Diaoyotai National Hotel yesterday. </seg>
<seg id=10> Production and assembling will be finished for all the equipments during this year. </seg>
</p>
